reviewText:
These are the real official home video versions of Wrestling Vixxxens: Wrestlerotica Vol. 1
They use to sell for $30.00+
These are must have dvd's the price are a real steal
If you grew up on WCW's late 80's early 90's Missy Hyatt
and WWF's early 90's mid 90's Tammy Sytch (Sunny) you're dig them
It's on par with decent Playboy videos
You also get the extreme woman of XPW  (This is very tame from where they came from)
Kristi Myst,
Jessica Darling,
Jasmin St. Claire (Yes that Jasmin St. Claire!)
The Wrestling Vixxxens site only put out two official home video dvd's
RF Video put out a cheap Behind the Scene style dvd  (Terrible this was only done for the owner of RF Video to sleep with Missy Hyatt)

Interesting Pro Wrestling time capsule also ahead of the time (Pre Celeb Leaked Sex Tapes) the overall concept/idea was ambitious
but, the technology was a bit to primitive to draw huge money plus there's all types of stories about the webmaster
who really knows! Snag them for $5.00 before they are out of print 9/10
Must have for Pro Wrestling fans or celeb sex tape fans
excellent nudes of the wrestlers. note no actual wrestling it self
